descr: "A statement of relationships from one set of concepts to one or more other concepts - either code systems or data elements, or classes in class models."

fields.name: property
fields.descr: "A reference to an element that holds a coded value that corresponds to a code system property. The idea is that the information model carries an element somwhere that is labeled to correspond with a code system property."

fields.name: system
fields.descr: "An absolute URI that identifies the code system of the dependency code (if the source/dependency is a value set that crosses code systems)."

fields.name: code
fields.descr: "Identity (code or path) or the element/item/ValueSet that the map depends on / refers to."

fields.name: display
fields.descr: "The display for the code. The display is only provided to help editors when editing the concept map."
